    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The quantity of water in a given substance; its weight as a percentage of the total dry weight of the material (as measured on the dry basis) or percentage of the weight per unit mass of the wet material (the wet basis). </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
